short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension solves the problem when chatgpt doesn't want to send your question with press enter

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension solves the problem of a bug on the chatgpt website that when the enter key is pressed the question written in the chat is expected to be sent but nothing happens, it simply does not work, with this extension this problem is solved in a simple way, it detects the enter key being pressed and a click on the button to send the question to the chat
